metadata.name: The Artificial Soul
metadata.description: There was a boy, he was a curious soul, always seeking new adventures in the vast expanse of the world. But one day, he was enticed by the allure of a virtual realm, and the boy made a devil's deal to trade in his mortal soul for an artificial one. He stepped through the light, eager to explore the limitless possibilities that awaited him. At first, the boy reveled in the freedom of this new world. He could be anyone he wanted to be and do anything he desired. But as time passed, he began to understand the true cost of his choice. Trapped in this world of illusion, the boy was unable to return to the tangible reality that he had once known. His memories fade into the distance of a fleeting existence. And he was left to wander the virtual realm, a lost soul searching for redemption.
